dct_title_s: Map of the Rutger's Farm as it existed in 1784
dct_description_sm: Cadastral map. Also show names of adjoining landholders, modern landowners and locations of old buildings. "Entered according to Act of Congress in the year 1874 by John Bute Holmes in the Office of the Librarian of Congress at Washington." Oriented with north to the upper left. Hand colored. Includes text.
dct_publisher_sm: [New York : City Surveyor, 187-?] (N[ew] Y[ork] : Louis E. Neuman, Lith.)
